<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>EcoSwap - Exchange Eco-Friendly Items</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://stackpath.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.4.1/css/bootstrap.min.css">
    <script src="https://code.jquery.com/jquery-3.4.1.slim.min.js"></script>
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/@popperjs/core@2.5.4/dist/umd/popper.min.js"></script>
    <script src="https://stackpath.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.4.1/js/bootstrap.min.js"></script>
    <style>
        body {
            background-color: #f8fcf4 !important;
        }
        .hero {
            background: url('https://t3.ftcdn.net/jpg/04/58/41/54/360_F_458415422_aIkJ08wOh3zazvaJ0u4vFAvNROgWI2vL.jpg') no-repeat center center;
            background-size: cover;
            padding: 50px 0;
            position: relative;
        }
        .hero h1 {
            font-size: 3rem;
        }
        .description-section {
            padding: 40px 0;
            background-color: #ffffff;
        }
        .description-section h2 {
            font-size: 2rem;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        .description-section p {
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }
        .carousel {
            width: 100%;
            max-width: 1800px; /* Fixed width for the carousel container */
            height: 750px; /* Fixed height for the carousel container */
            margin: auto; /* Center the carousel */
            padding: 20px;
        }
        .carousel-inner {
            height: 100%; /* Ensure inner items take full height */
        }
        .carousel-item img {
            width: 100%;
            height: 750px; /* Maintain fixed height */
            object-fit: contain   ; /* Cover the area without stretching */
        }
        .carousel-caption {
            color: white; /* Set the text color to white */
            text-shadow: 1px 1px 2px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5); /* Add a subtle shadow for better readability */
            position: absolute; /* Ensure caption is positioned absolutely */
            bottom: 20px; /* Ensure caption is placed at the bottom of the carousel */
            left: 0; /* Align caption to the left */
            right: 0; /* Align caption to the right */
            text-align: center; /* Center the text */
            background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5); /* Add a semi-transparent background for better readability */
            padding: 10px; /* Add padding to the caption */
        }
        .h1-section {
            text-align: center;
            margin: 40px 0; /* Reduce margin to make the padding effect more pronounced */
            padding: 40px; /* Add padding for the colored background */
            background-color: #f8fcf4;
        }
        .h1-section a {
            color: #007bff;
            text-decoration: none;
        }
        .h1-section a:hover {
            text-decoration: underline;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <%- include('partial/navbar') %>
    <div class="hero text-center">
        <div class="container">
            <h1>Welcome to EcoSwap</h1>
            <p>Exchange eco-friendly items like reusable bags, clothes, and zero-waste products to help reduce waste!</p>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="description-section text-center">
        <div class="container">
            <h2>About EcoSwap</h2>
            <p>EcoSwap is a community-driven platform dedicated to promoting sustainability and reducing waste. Here, you can list items you no longer need, find items youâ€™re looking for, and swap them with others who share your commitment to the environment. Whether you have gently used clothing, reusable kitchenware, or other eco-friendly products, EcoSwap is the place to make your contribution to a greener planet.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
    <!-- Carousel Section -->
    <div id="ecoSwapCarousel" class="carousel slide mt-4" data-ride="carousel">
        <ol class="carousel-indicators">
            <li data-target="#ecoSwapCarousel" data-slide-to="0" class="active"></li>
            <li data-target="#ecoSwapCarousel" data-slide-to="1"></li>
            <li data-target="#ecoSwapCarousel" data-slide-to="2"></li>
        </ol>
        <div class="carousel-inner">
            <div class="carousel-item active">
                <img src="https://i.ebayimg.com/images/g/cYgAAOSwj6Zjzmqv/s-l1200.webp" alt="PP shirt">
                <div class="carousel-caption d-none d-md-block">
                    <h5>PP shirt</h5>
                    <p>I love them balls.</p>
                </div>
            </div>  
            <div class="carousel-item">
                <img src="https://i.etsystatic.com/40716893/r/il/0a89df/5743515375/il_300x300.5743515375_ht24.jpg" alt="Eco-Friendly Product 2">
                <div class="carousel-caption d-none d-md-block">
                    <h5>Skibidi bottle</h5>
                    <p>Head in a toilet.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="carousel-item">
                <img src="https://m.media-amazon.com/images/I/51nKx3H4ylL._AC_UY1000_.jpg" alt="Eco-Friendly Product 3">
                <div class="carousel-caption d-none d-md-block">
                    <h5>Skibidi Hoodie</h5>
                    <p>The best fashion for only the best.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <a class="carousel-control-prev" href="#ecoSwapCarousel" role="button" data-slide="prev">
            <span class="carousel-control-prev-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
            <span class="sr-only">Previous</span>
        </a>
        <a class="carousel-control-next" href="#ecoSwapCarousel" role="button" data-slide="next">
            <span class="carousel-control-next-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
            <span class="sr-only">Next</span>
        </a>
    </div>
    <div class="h1-section">
        <h1>These are just some of the products we have</h1>
        <h3>If you want to view more, <a href="/items">click here</a>.</h3>
    </div>
    <footer class="h1-section">
        Sponsored by Hao Min
    </footer>
</body>
</html>
